short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Web Clipper allows you to send messages to your N8N instance or Discord or any othere APP via predefined WebHook profiles.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
I developed this extension as a small test, and it's almost entirely crafted by AI using the 'Cline' and 'Aider' extensions. Initially, it was meant to be a simple tool for sending links to the N8N program, but it eventually gained additional features like profiles, background customization, and a tag booster that allows for quick and easy tag addition. All config can be easy backup, save and edit as it is visible in configuration as JSON dump.

The extension allows configuration of various profiles, and the ability to define custom URLs and body content makes it versatile for different purposes.

Feel free to share any improvement ideas, errors, or suggestions on GitHub.

A synthetic creation has produced a functioning work.
